results indicate\nthat high-level metrics such as array porosity may not be sufficient on their\nown for predicting wake and drag characteristics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Feb 2022 19:33:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Apr 2023 17:04:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-03"}
