 demonstrates the need for studying the turbulent dynamo in\na multiphase medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Feb 2022 20:41:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 May 2022 04:21:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-01"}
