sis of this\nmode, there is no coupling observed but this the convective cell mode evolves\nwhereas nonlinear dynamics of this mode are found to obey the vortex-like\nsolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Feb 2022 21:09:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-18"}
