ignals with\naveraged periods of 4.10 $\\pm$ 0.04 yr and 7.57 $\\pm$ 0.03 yr can be clearly\nobserved. Finally, in both signals, periods are slightly longer for plages in\ncomparison with sunspots.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Feb 2022 12:24:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-30"}
